title: Valar Rereadis: The Sworn Sword - Part 3
description:
In this episode: Living in a post Blackfyre world, Rohanne, love for Addam, love for Daemon, love for Daenerys. So much love you'll forget there's a drought! How Rohanne fits into the Lannister family tree, Aemon the Dragonknight, Bittersteel, Kingsguard foreshadowing, the sneaky Septon Sefton scene and some of the funniest moments.
